Owner's suite has recently updated 3/4 ensuite bathroom. Numerous upgrades inc 50-year roof (inst 2007); 2nd furnace, & AC. Plenty of room to spread out inside & out - large garden space ready to go for next spring, large driveway, on extra wide street. Truly a must see home!

This exquisitely designed duplex, occupied by young professionals, is a South Hill investment gem. Featuring 3 beds on the main, w/ month-to-month lease, a gas furnace, & updated kitchen & bath, it is an ideal opp for owner-occupancy. Live-edge shelving, FP insert, fir floors, & Marmoleum plank in the living spaces will captivate. The upper unit offers vaulted ceilings w/ 2-bed layout, 3/4 bath & standalone gas FP. Guests can savor the urban & territorial views, complemented by a glimpse of the water. Steps from downtown Bellingham & the university, this Craftsman home boasts a fully fenced yard, perfect for entertaining in both the front and back; complete with flagstone patio, garden shed, & 3 car parking pad with a garage off the alley.

Welcome to Cottonwood Beach in Birch Bay. This 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom home is a blend of historic charm with modern amenities. Completely updated. Kitchen just updated with a brand-new stainless-steel dishwasher, refrigerator, deep sink as well as butcher block counter tops. Front entrance opens up to high ceilings and cozy fireplace creating a compelling living space. Large open back yard surrounded by tall cedars offering a peaceful and private setting. Three outbuildings for additional storage options. This home sits on a lot and a half with possibilities of a garage/ADU adding more versatility (verify with the City of Blaine) A tranquil retreat located on a no through road and a five-minute walk to Halverson Public Beach

Located in coveted Samish neighborhood near Lk Padden, Galbraith Mtn., I-5 and shopping. The cute front porch welcomes you into a generous foyer, the perfect place to sit, take off your shoes and coat transitioning from your day into home-mode. The easy flowing floor plan and elegant finishes are relaxing. There is plenty of natural light and the remote controlled shades on the main level make it easy to set the vibe or keep the sun out, even from afar. Your well appointed kitchen has ample built-in storage and double ovens. French doors open to the cute and private back yard. This home has enough outdoor space to enjoy, garden and landscape to your hearts desire, or keep it low maintenance and kick back. Welcome to your new home.

Charming 3-bed, 2-bath log home in the serene Sudden Valley community! This single-level cabin-in-the-woods style home offers a cozy, rustic feel with an open floor plan and large deck for outdoor entertaining. Situated on a spacious lot backing up to lush greenspace, you'll enjoy the peaceful surroundings and abundant wildlife. Perfect for first-time buyers or those looking for a clean slate to make their own, the home also includes two small outbuildings for storage or hobbies. Enjoy the quiet, nature-filled lifestyle, all while being close to community amenities like the lake, trails, and parks. A must-see!

Welcome to the beloved Snowater resort - 20 acres of lush forest, 2000 feet of riverfront, and 4 seasons of Pacific Northwest adventure await your arrival! Meticulously maintained, this spacious one bedroom, one bathroom condo is your go-to recreational spot and investment opportunity to cherish for years to come! Lots of hiking, boating, fishing, snowshoeing. Resort grounds include multiple tennis/pickle ball/basketball courts, indoor swimming pools, jacuzzis, indoor pickle ball/racketball courts, indoor and outdoor playgrounds and children's play areas, fitness center, sun decks. BBQ picnic area, Log Cabin for reading/studying, walking paths surround the property.
